  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Remove the <strong>coconut cream</strong> from the sachet<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> and chop roughly</p><p>Add the chopped coconut cream,<strong> lime leaves</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a large pan, stir in 500ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat - this is your <strong>poaching liquid</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>rice</strong>, 400ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a pot with a matching lid, over a high heat</p><p>Cover and cook for 10 min, or until almost all the water is absorbed</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel the <strong>ginger</strong> (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate)</p><p>Add the ginger to the <strong>poaching liquid</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut each <strong>fish fillet</strong> into 3 equal portions and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Pick the <strong>leaves</strong> off the <strong>coriander</strong> stalks and set them aside for garnish</p><p>Chop the <strong>stems</strong> finely and add them to the <strong>poaching liquid</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/555.-step-4-x700.jpg",
