    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, transfer the <strong>poached fish</strong> to a plate (it's OK if you get some mushrooms)</p><p>Add the cooked <strong>rice</strong> to the<strong> poaching liquid</strong>, stir to combine - this is your <strong>tom kha rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
